Feline2::

She heard the loud thump behind her. She turned and was hit. She fell 
to the ground with a large chest wound. She got up slowly, groaning 
from the pain. She looked and saw the hole in her armor, leaking 
badly. She stood up and growled at Fury. She transformed into leopard 
mode and went to HotRod. She stood next to him, growling at Fury.
"You have no right to attack! We were not attacking or hurting 
anything! You had no right!" she growled loudly at him.
